Package cz.cuni.mff.mozharon.financialaccounting.infrastructure.common

Class ServiceContainer

java.lang.Object
cz.cuni.mff.mozharon.financialaccounting.infrastructure.common.ServiceContainer
public class ServiceContainer extends Object
Container for centralizing the management of service instances within the application. This class provides a unified access point for retrieving various services that are used throughout the application, facilitating easy management of dependencies.
